data.description: A great home in the heart of Historic Barberton! Plenty of space in this well maintained colonial that boasts 3 bedrooms and a full basement. Lots of updates throughout, including new floors and cabinets. The basement is waterproofed with a transferrable warranty, and the home is move-in ready!
